narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Material very relevant, great student participation. Prof is fantastic but doesn't speak enough.
Tell us to do more activities/debates in the presentations from the beginning - we'd figured it out by halfway through but it was more interesting than just listening to the Prezi

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Emma is a queen take the course off of the simple fact that you get to spend 2 hours sitting with her every week!
One of the best classes offered at Yale. Emma Sky is brilliant, and you will learn so much from her.
Absolutely. Great material prof Sky made it great.
AMAZING COURSE. DEF TAKE IT. You are honored to be in the same room as her- take this class!!

Yes, if you want to develop a more nuanced understanding of current and recent issues in the Middle East then this is an incredible course. Do not take it if you simply want a survey of political history in the Middle East - that is more background to the current events.
